name: Lulu (Final Fantasy X) NSFW 3D
description:
Hello friends, this is my first LoRA and I'm glad to introduce Lulu from Final Fantasy X to you.

This is NSFW model with mostly open dressed, lingerie and naked variants.

LoRA was trained on Perfect world model with 3D NSFW/SFW arts.

2nd ver was trained on animefill-pruned.ckpt.

Also second alt. version was trained on "vanilla" SD 1.5 for best compitability with realistic models like Deliberate v2.

V1.1 is also good! If you like it more - use it. But it was made without trigger words and more with deepbooru interrogates.

60 arts were used (4000 (2000 with batch size 2) steps with 10 epoches).

0.75-0.9 strength of Lora is the best radius.

Clip skip 2 for anime-based models and clip skip 1 for realistic SD1.5 models.

Some necessary Waifu diffusion prompt for better experience:

LuluFFX, mature female, eyebrows behind hair, hair over one eye, covered eye

black hair, hair stick, hair bun,

For dress:

black dress, strapless, bare shoulders, fur trim.

If you have troubles with distorted eyes or bangs:

  • use highres.fix (I prefer not to do this);

  • use SD Upscale script in img2img (For me 1.25-1.5x with AnimeSharp or UltraSharp is good on 0.2-0.3 denoising strengh);

  • Use inpaint (but with SD Upscale and dddetailer I don't need this in 90% times);

  • Use Photoshop.

I will be glad to receive feedback from you and a demonstration of your art with my LoRA!

My other LoRA works: https://civitai.com/user/Enigmata/models

https://tensor.art/u/604375505701151021
